            <p>Our Oncosurgery Department works closely with other specialty departments, including medical oncology, radiation oncology, pathology, radiology, and supportive care services, to provide comprehensive cancer care to our patients. We collaborate in multidisciplinary tumor boards to develop individualized treatment plans tailored to each patient's unique cancer diagnosis, stage, and treatment goals.</p>
